  <a class="cta-button" href="/enquiry">Get a Quote</a>
  </div>
  </section><!-- MAIN CONTENT SECTION --><section class="service-detail">
  <div class="box-container">
  <h2>Your Local Surveyor in Guilden Sutton</h2>
  <p>
          Based just minutes away, I carry out building surveys throughout Guilden Sutton and nearby villages. Whether you're buying a period property or inspecting a modern home, I provide clear, RICS-aligned reports with fast turnaround and no jargon.
        </p>
  <h2>Surveying Services Available</h2>
  <ul>
  <li><strong>RICS Level 1 Condition Report:</strong> For newer or well-maintained homes needing a basic condition summary.</li>
  <li><strong>RICS Level 2 HomeBuyer Report:</strong> Popular for standard homes—includes condition ratings, repair advice and maintenance tips.</li>
  <li><strong>RICS Level 3 Building Survey:</strong> In-depth analysis of structure, materials, and repair priorities—ideal for older or extended properties.</li>
  <li><strong>Damp &amp; Timber Inspections:</strong> Identify moisture problems, decay, and mould with practical recommendations.</li>
  <li><strong>Ventilation Assessments:</strong> Check airflow, air quality and causes of condensation in residential properties.</li>
  <li><strong>Measured Floorplans:</strong> Accurate plans for planning, resale, or extensions.</li>
  </ul>
  <h2>Why Choose LEM?</h2>
  <ul>
  <li><strong>AssocRICS-qualified:</strong> Trusted, experienced and independent — no sales or upsells.</li>
  <li><strong>Fast reporting:</strong> Most survey reports delivered within 3–5 working days.</li>
  <li><strong>Local knowledge:</strong> Experienced with construction types common across Guilden Sutton and the Chester area.</li>
  </ul>
  <h2>Get a Quote Today</h2>
  <p>
          Whether you're ready to book or just comparing survey options, I’m happy to provide guidance and a tailored quote. No pressure — just honest help.
        </p>
  <div class="cta-section">
  <a class="cta-button" href="/enquiry">Request a Quote</a>
  <a class="secondary-button" href="/comparison">Compare Survey Levels</a>
  </div>
  </div>
